column5: Bugs are out here(Montreal area)big time.....
How's the walleye bite with that hatch, Larry?
Oh man, that's brutal.  I had to defend myself on Sunday out there with the bug swarms, but they were only small ones.  Still annoying tho!  Joey
The skeeters were out in full force this weekend on GBay. Thankfully we don't have any black flies. Hopefully with the heat and dryness they won't last too long.
wow, that looks like horror movie scene!
